title: SIXTEEN | Main Event & Contest Results
body_text:
If you missed ECD's 16th birthday or simply want to relive some of the memorable moments, let's get you started with the trifecta of main attractions!
Numerous age-related records were broken, including Max's improbable Championship Chase victory!
